Ammara Mahomed was the lucky winner of the Buxxi/Tabloid Newspapers helicopter competition that was held recently. Despite butterflies in her stomach the brave Durban lass took to the skies this weekend catching a glimpse of Durban’s golden mile with a birds eye view. ” A helicopter ride was always something on my bucket list and I finally got to scratch it off. Thanks to Buxxi and Tabloid Newspapers, I had one of the most flabbergasting experiences,”  said the ecstatic Ammara.